\id JON - Mutu (Saveeng-Oov) NT [tuc] -Papua New Guinea 2011 (web version -2013)
\h Yona
\toc1 YONA
\toc2 Yona
\toc3 Yona
\mt1 YONA
\mt2 Jona—Jonah
\c 1
\s1 Yona izoor Maaron aliŋa
\p 
\v 1 Ŋgeu eez, iza Yona. Ye Amitai natu. Sawa eez, Yoova aliŋa ila pani ighaze:
\v 2 “Umundig ula pa ndug tiina Ninive, \f + \fr 1:2 \ft Ninive, nene ndug tiina to yes Asiria. Ineep mala kat pa Israel dige ila pa ndag iza. Yes Israela lolodi pa yes Asiria rita maau, ve timatughez padi. Pasa, yes Asiria tiraua kat pa ghamuuŋ malmal. \f*
\m ve uvotia aliŋag padi. Usaav padi ughaze: Ŋgar todi samsamia, you Yoova naghita di tisob wa. Tovenen you pale naghur atia padi pa sosor todi.”
\p 
\v 3 Eemoghon Yona itaaru, ve lolo pa ila Ninive maau. Tovenen ighaze iyooŋ pa Yoova, ve ighau ila pa ndug mala eez iza Tarsis. Ye ilaagh izila naari le ila peria ndug Yoppa. Ghoro ighita waaŋ eez to ighaze ila pa ndug Tarsis. \f + \fr 1:3 \ft Ndug Tarsis ineep mala kat pa Israel dige ila pa ndag izila, ve ndug Ninive ineep ila pa ndag iza. Tovenen tipargharau maau. Tineep saguan saguan kat. \f*
\m Ye ighol waaŋ atia le isob, ghoro iza waaŋ tonowen, leso ighau pa Yoova ve ila. \rq Mbo 139:7 \rq*
\p 
\v 4 Tiraav tila, ve Yoova igham yaghur tiina imundig le ipei dibom iza toman tapiri. Ve rismoghon tone timbiriis.
\v 5 Tovenen matughezaaŋ tiina igham uraata to waaŋ, ve yes eŋaeŋa titaŋ roran maaron todi todi, leso tiuul di. Eemoghon te isami le isami kat. Tauto tipiyaav mburuguuŋ tisob tila pa te, leso waaŋ pokia iza. Yona ikankaan pa pataŋani to ivot. Pasa, izila waaŋ lolo to sila we, ve izi igheen le lolo imaagh kat.
\p 
\v 6 Tovenen ŋgeu to igham pooz pa waaŋ izila toni, ve isaav pani ighaze: “Wai, ukaria ghenooŋ wa! Umundig ve anam utoov utaŋ roran maaron tiom ve taghita! Pale irau iuul ghiit, ma maau. Pasa, paam talaleed.”
\p 
\v 7 Ghoro yes uraata to waaŋ tiwasavon di tighaze: “Ai! Iit irau taŋgozŋgooz, leso taghita sei kat to inim pughu pa pataŋani tonene!” Tovenen tiŋgozŋgooz le ŋgozŋgozaaŋ todi ipatooŋ Yona ighaze ye to inim pughu pa pataŋani tonenen.
\v 8 Tovenen tighasoni tighaze: “Usaav ghazooŋa payei lak! Pughu vena to pataŋani tonene ivot pait? Ve yom ulaagh pa sa uraat? Yom to sa ndug. Uneep sine to unum?”
\p 
\v 9-10 Tovenen Yona ipamuul aliŋadi ighaze: “You to Hibru. Nambesmbees pa Yoova. Ye Maaron to sambam to ighur te ve taan. Eemoghon naghau pani ve nanim.” Tilooŋ saveeŋ tonene, le matughezaaŋ tiina igham di. Tovenen tisaav pani tighaze: “Wai, yom ugham sosor tiina kat!
\v 11 Pale nigham vena payom, leso te imaat, ve taun izi pait?” Pasa, te isami le isami kat.
\p 
\v 12 Yona ipamuul aliŋadi ighaze: “Asur ghou ve apiyaav ghou nazila pa te. Leso taun izi. Pasa, nene sosor tiou, tauto pataŋani tonene ivot.”
\v 13 Yes uraata to waaŋ lolodi pa tipiyaava izila pa te rikia maau. Tighaze ineep ve titoov ŋgoraaŋ tilooŋ tila pa taan. Tiŋgoor tiŋgoor, eemoghon tiraua maau. Pasa, ndug isami le isami kat.
\v 14 Tovenen tighaze tipiyaav Yona izila pa te. Eemoghon timatughez pa tigham tovene. Tauto titaŋ roran Yoova tighaze: “O Yoova, ighaze nipiyaav ŋgeu tonene izila te ve imaat, uwaghamun ghei nimaat malep. Ughita ghei ughaze yei nigham sosor malep. Pasa, yei lolomai pa nirab ŋgeu tonene maau. Yom to ugham mbeb tonene ivot itaghon taum lolom ve ŋgar tiom.”
\p 
\v 15 Ghoro tisur Yona ve tipiyaava izila pa te, ve rikia moghon yaghur toman dibom ate izi, ve taun izi.
\v 16 Yes uraata to waaŋ tighita mbeb tonenen, le timatughez kat pa Yoova. Ve tigham watooŋrau pani, toman saveeŋ mbuaaŋ ariaŋa pida paam.
\p 
\v 17 Ghoro Yoova imbaaŋ iigh tiina eez ila ve itoon Yona. Tovenen Yona ineep ila iigh apo lolo irau mboŋ tol. \rq Mt 12:40, 16:4 \rq*
\c 2
\s1 Suŋuuŋ to Yona
\p 
\v 1 Yona inepneep ila iigh tiina apo lolo, ve isuŋ pa Maaron toni Yoova ighaze:
\q1 
\v 2 “Sawa to nanepneep ila pataŋani tiina lolo, you nataŋ roran Yoova.
\q2 Ve ye ilooŋ aliŋag ve iuul ghou.
\q2 Yoova, you nanepneep ila ndug to yes mateeŋa, ve taŋiiz tiou iŋarua ghom naghaze uul ghou.
\q2 Ve yom ulooŋ taŋiiz tiou.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Yom upandalin ghou le nazila mazovan to sila kat we.
\q2 Ve te itatab ghou, ve waŋaar ighereb ghou nala nanim,
\q2 ve dibom tiom tintina tipol tizala poghog.
\b
\q1 
\v 4 You nagham ŋgar naghaze yom undiir ghou pa naghom wa.
\q2 Eemoghon naghur ila naghaze pale naghita rumai tiom patabuaŋ muul.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Dibom ipol izala poghog, ve itatab ghou.
\q2 Ve waŋaar to te lolo ililiit ghou, ve aniiŋ to pon ikaukau dabag.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 You nazila lolooz pughu to sila we.
\q2 Ndug samia tonowen ikis ghou le nagham ŋgar naghaze irau naza muul maau.
\q2 Eemoghon Maaron tiou Yoova, yom undae ghou naza.
\q2 Tauto namaat ve nazila ndug to mateeŋa maau, ve aazne naneep matag iyaryaar.
\q1 
\v 7 “Yoova, sawa to tapirig ighaze isob, you matag iŋgal ghom, ve suŋuuŋ tiou iŋarua ghom.
\q2 Ve yom unepneep ila rumai tiom patabuaŋ lolo, ve ulooŋ ghou.
\q1 
\v 8 “Yes to timbesmbees pa maaron kaaromŋa, tighur muridi pa poia to Maaron.
\q2 Tauto irau tighita anoŋa eta maau.
\q1 
\v 9 “Eemoghon you lolog poia pa ulaaŋ tiom. Tovenen nambou pa napait ghom, ve nagham watooŋrau payom.
\q2 Ve mbeb tisob to nambua saveeŋ toman ghom pa nagham di, you pale nagham di.
\q2 Yoova, yom moghon to Volaaŋa tiou.”
\p 
\v 10 Ghoro Yoova isaav pa iigh tiina tonowen, ve ila iluar Yona izi naari.
\c 3
\s1 Yona itaghon Maaron aliŋa ve ila pa ndug tiina Ninive
\p 
\v 1-2 Ghoro Yoova aliŋa ila muul pa Yona inim pae ru. Isaav pani ighaze: “Umundig, ve ula pa ndug tiina Ninive, ve uvotia saveeŋ to you nasavia payom ne padi.”
\p 
\v 3 Tovenen Yona itaghon Yoova aliŋa, ve imundig ila pa Ninive. Ninive, nene ndug tiina kat. Ighaze tala talib pa ndug dige ite, nene pale talaagh ndag tol ma venen.
\p 
\v 4 Yona ila peria ve ilooŋ ila ndug tiina. Ilaagh irau ndag eez, ve itetem pa Yoova aliŋa ighaze: “Mboŋ tamoot ru tonene ighaze isob, Yoova pale ireu ndug Ninive le imbiriis.”
\p 
\v 5 Yes Ninivea tilooŋ saveeŋ tonene, le tighur ila to Maaron. Yes tighilaal sosor todi, ve lolodi ipataŋan pani. Tovenen tigham saveeŋ tighaze yes tisob irau tiŋgun taudi pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ, ve tindud di pa nonogiiŋa to moŋiiŋ. Yes to izadi tintina, ve itaghoni taghoni izi pa yes to izadi maau ne paam. \rq Mt 12:41; Lu 11:32 \rq*
\p 
\v 6 Kinik to Ninive ilooŋ Yona varu, ve ye paam ipul ina to ghamuuŋ pooz, ve iduduum nonogiiŋa toni poia izi, ve indudi pa uli to moŋiiŋ, ghoro mbole izala avab.
\p 
\v 7 Ve aliŋa ila pa yes Ninivea ighaze: “You kinik yeiŋa daba tiou nighur tutuuŋ ariaŋa tovene: Iit tamtoghon pale tasob taŋgun tauud pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ ve ghunuuŋ ya. Ve ŋgai toit tovene paam. Makau, sipsip, ve ŋgai to naol ne, tilaagh malep, tighan ve tighun malep. Iit tasob taneep sorok tovene.
\v 8 Ve iit tamtoghon toman ŋgai toit pale tatatab ghiit pa uli to moŋiiŋ, ve iit eŋaeŋa tataŋ roran Maaron ariaŋa. Ve taghur muriid pa ŋgar toit samsamia, ve tapul didiaaŋ toit toman ŋgar to rabuuŋ tamtoghon ineeple.
\v 9 Ve taghita. Maaron pale itoor ŋgar toni, ma maau? Ighaze ye itatan mbalmbali toni, ve lolo isamin ghiit, nene pale tamaat maau.”
\p 
\v 10 Maaron ighita yes Ninivea tipul ŋgar todi samsamia ve titoor gabuadi, tauto lolo isamin di, ve iwaghamun di maau. Atia to muuŋ ye ighaze ighuri padi, nene ighami maau. \rq Igham 32:14 \rq*
\c 4
\s1 Yona ate yabyab, tauto Maaron ipaghazoŋani pa poia toni
\p 
\v 1 Yona ighita mbeb to ivot ne, le irau lolo maau. Ate yabyab kat pasa, Yoova lolo isamin yes Ninivea, ve irab di maau.
\p 
\v 2 Tovenen isuŋ pa Yoova ighaze: “O Yoova, sawa to nanepneep izi ndug tiou sone, you nawatag wa. Yom pale ugham tovene. Tauto naghaze naghau rikia moghon nala pa ndug Tarsis. Pasa, you nawatag: Yom Maaron to lolom isasamin tamtoghon, ve ughamgham poian di. Atem yabyab rikia maau. Yom lolom ineep tuŋia ila to tamtoghon, ve ughaze ughur poia tiom iza todi. Tovenen ighaze tamtoghon tipul ŋgar todi samsamia, yom irau ughur pataŋani padi maau. \rq Igham 34:6 \rq*
\m 
\v 3 Tovenen Yoova, naghaze poia pa namaat ve ugham ghou nalat to aazne. Lolog pa naneep muul maau.”
\p 
\v 4 Eemoghon Yoova ipamuul aliŋa ighaze: “Yona, ughita. Malmaliiŋ tiom tonanan deŋia?”
\v 5 Eemoghon Yona isavia saveeŋ eta maau. Neneeŋa moghon. Ve ipul ndug tiina, ve ivot ila pumuri, ve ila ineep Ninive dige to ila pa ndag iza. Ghoro ipayoon le dur tonowe, leso ineep ila samba, ve ate izi. Ve isasaŋan ighaze ighita sa mbeb pale ivot pa ndug tiina Ninive.
\p 
\v 6 Ghoro Maaron igham waar eez itub iza, leso inim yavyaav pa Yona, ve ipoona pa ndag. Yona ighita waar tonowen, le lolo poia kat.
\v 7 Eemoghon mboŋ ndugizau, ghoro Maaron imbaaŋ motmoot tighan waar tonenen le igorgor.
\v 8 Sawa to ndag iza, Maaron igham yaghur ghaughauru ilaagh toman tuntunu. Ve ndag ighaaz Yona daba, le tapiri isob ve ighaze imaat. Tovenen isaav ighaze: “Wais, lolog pa naneep muul maau. Namaat, ghoro poia!”
\p 
\v 9 Eemoghon Maaron isaav pani ighaze: “Waar tonanan igorgor, tauto atem yabyab ve uŋooŋ ne? Ughita. Ŋoŋaaŋ tiom tonene, deŋia?”
\p Yona ipamuul aliŋa ighaze: “Vee, malmaliiŋ tiou, nene deŋia. Tauto naghaze namaat, ghoro poia.”
\p 
\v 10 Tovenen Yoova isaav pani muul ighaze: “Waar tonanan, itub iza inim tiina pa mboŋ ee moghon. Ve ndag ite ila rabrab izi, waar igorgor. Yom ugham uraat pani maau. Ye tau itub iza. Eemoghon yom lolom isamin waar tonanan sorok, ve ugham ŋgar tiina pani.
\v 11 Ughita. Ninive, nene ndug tiina kat, ve tamtoghona ival le ival kat. Tilib pa 120,000. Ve yes ledi ghilalooŋ maau. Ŋgar todi inimale ndipain to irau tighilaal ŋgar samia ve ŋgar poia ne maau. Ve ŋgai todi paam, katindi. Vena, irau nagham ŋgar padi ve lolog isamin di maau?” 
